---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Services – AngloEdge" description="Custom research, consulting, and advisory services for institutional investors and corporate strategists.">
  <article class="max-w-prose mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <header class="mb-12">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Services</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">
        Beyond daily briefings, we provide institutional-grade intelligence tailored to your specific strategic needs.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-16">
      {/* Market Research */}
      <section class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-12">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Market Research & Custom Reports</h2>
        <p>
          We produce deep-dive research on specific sectors, regulatory regimes, and market structures. Recent work has covered gilt market mechanics, SME financing dynamics, pension fund positioning, and consolidation trends across mid-cap equity.
        </p>
        <p>
          These aren't generic equity research reports. We provide the reasoning that institutional investors and corporate strategy teams actually need: market structure analysis, incentive mapping, competitive dynamics, and forward-looking scenarios.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600 text-sm">
          Custom research typically ranges from £5,000–£25,000 depending on scope and depth. Timeline: 2–4 weeks.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <a href="/contact?service=research" class="inline-block px-4 py-2 border border-navy text-navy hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition-colors text-sm font-medium">
            Discuss a project
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* Speaking */}
      <section class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-12">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Speaking & Events</h2>
        <p>
          We speak at industry conferences, investor forums, corporate board sessions, and private roundtables on UK capital markets strategy, regulatory trends, and emerging market risks.
        </p>
        <p>
          Engagements are bespoke to your audience. We don't deliver canned presentations. Whether you need a keynote on gilt market dynamics for a pension fund conference, or a boardroom session on competitor positioning for a corporate strategy team, we tailor the content to your specific context and decision-making priorities.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600 text-sm">
          Speaking fees and format are customized by engagement type and audience size. For premium events or multi-day engagements, we offer package discounts.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <a href="/contact?service=speaking" class="inline-block px-4 py-2 border border-navy text-navy hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition-colors text-sm font-medium">
            Discuss an event
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* Bespoke Intelligence */}
      <section class="pb-12">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Bespoke Intelligence & Advisory</h2>
        <p>
          For institutional clients managing significant capital or executives navigating strategic decisions, we offer ongoing intelligence services: quarterly research subscriptions, real-time market alerts, regulatory impact analysis, and confidential advisory on UK market structure and competitive dynamics.
        </p>
        <p>
          This is intelligence built to your specific mandate. M&A teams need different analysis than macro investors. Corporate treasurers need different insights than hedge funds. We build research workflows tailored to your business.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600 text-sm">
          Retainer arrangements start at £15,000/quarter and scale based on scope. Minimum 3-month engagement.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <a href="/contact?service=advisory" class="inline-block px-4 py-2 border border-navy text-navy hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition-colors text-sm font-medium">
            Schedule a call
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* Inquiry */}
      <section class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-12 mt-12">
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Who We Work With</h3>
        <p>
          Our clients include institutional investors (long-only and alternative), corporate development teams, asset managers, financial advisors, and policy participants. If you manage capital or make strategic decisions in UK markets, we can help.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Have a specific project in mind? <a href="/contact" class="text-navy hover:underline">Get in touch</a>. No obligation, no pressure. We'll discuss what you need and whether we're the right fit.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  h2 {
    @apply font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-4;
  }

  h3 {
    @apply font-serif text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-4;
  }

  p {
    @apply leading-tight text-gray-900 mb-4;
  }

  a {
    @apply text-navy hover:underline;
  }

  section {
    @apply mb-8;
  }
</style>
